column4: Big Cisco bet on France offers relief from Air France fiasco
column5: PARIS Still reeling from front page images of shirtless Air France executives fleeing angry workers  the French government got a welcome boost on Thursday for its campaign to attract foreign investment from U.S. tech group Cisco.
